parameters":{"content":"### Weekly Schedule\n\nStarts the workflow on a timer — weekly. No input data; downstream nodes fetch what they need.\n\nNext: Stamp & Shape Post","width":280,"height":232,"color":5},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[-330,520],"id":"b4f22953-9499-80cc-72fd-fada2d38bd37","name":"Note: Weekly Schedule"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Stamp & Shape Post\n\nShapes the item: writes `postId`, `receivedAt`. Keeps the schema explicit between stages.\n\nNext: Payload Valid?","width":280,"height":232,"color":7},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[-6,520],"id":"37ffe31d-05b2-c9d2-0165-3fbc3400c184","name":"Note: Stamp & Shape Post"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Payload Valid?\n\nTwo-way gate on `={{ $json.postId }}`. TRUE continues the happy path, FALSE takes the alternate branch.\n\nPorts: ①→ Build the Brief · ②→ Record Rejected Input","width":280,"height":232,"color":2},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[318,520],"id":"00909c43-96a8-bde5-a127-b63413f6656b","name":"Note: Payload Valid?"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Record Rejected Input\n\ngoogleSheets — `append` operation against the connected account.\n\n↻ retries 3×/2s · 🔑 Google OAuth2 / service account","width":280,"height":232,"color":2},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[318,1030],"id":"50c83f06-07d4-a1e1-752d-3e934766aefd","name":"Note: Record Rejected Input"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Build the Brief\n\nShapes the item: writes `brief`, `tone`. Keeps the schema explicit between stages.\n\nNext: Draft with AI Writer","width":280,"height":232,"color":7},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[642,520],"id":"189669c1-5925-8759-a3b0-7c1b94a89263","name":"Note: Build the Brief"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Draft with AI Writer\n\nSingle fixed LLM step (no tool choice) — cheaper and more predictable than an agent.\n\nPorts: ①→ Refine with AI Editor · ②→ Capture Failure Context\n\n⚠ failures exit via the error rail","width":280,"height":232,"color":6},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[966,520],"id":"c6c1c774-3ab2-b01b-f587-22d6eece4a91","name":"Note: Draft with AI Writer"},{"parameters":{"content":"### OpenAI Writer Model\n\nChat model powering the AI step (model: `gpt-4o-mini`). Swap providers here without rewiring.\n\nFeeds **Draft with AI Writer** as `languageModel`\n\n🔑 OpenAI API key","width":280,"height":232,"color":6},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[1209,1090],"id":"e25e5cb2-8332-d2ac-334c-59b01fd361be","name":"Note: OpenAI Writer Model"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Refine with AI Editor\n\nSingle fixed LLM step (no tool choice) — cheaper and more predictable than an agent.\n\nPorts: ①→ Convert to HTML · ②→ Capture Failure Context\n\n⚠ failures exit via the error rail","width":280,"height":232,"color":6},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[1533,520],"id":"b481c19e-8699-85c5-3d8b-45851e585a45","name":"Note: Refine with AI Editor"},{"parameters":{"content":"### OpenAI Editor Model\n\nChat model powering the AI step (model: `gpt-4o-mini`). Swap providers here without rewiring.\n\nFeeds **Refine with AI Editor** as `languageModel`\n\n🔑 OpenAI API key","width":280,"height":232,"color":6},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[1776,1090],"id":"dec6baae-342d-639a-b83c-9f1e70e1f698","name":"Note: OpenAI Editor Model"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Convert to HTML\n\nConverts markdown to HTML for rich rendering in email/CMS.\n\nNext: Publish Draft to WordPress","width":280,"height":232,"color":2},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[2100,520],"id":"a93eec1b-9b5c-c66a-fcd6-eb55f1d7d43a","name":"Note: Convert to HTML"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Publish Draft to WordPress\n\nwordpress — `action` operation against the connected account.\n\nPorts: ①→ Save Execution Metadata · ②→ Capture Failure Context\n\n↻ retries 3×/2s · ⚠ failures exit via the error rail · 🔑 WordPress credentials","width":280,"height":232,"color":4},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[2424,520],"id":"431b33b5-4d00-cda3-5cbe-3fff4f978103","name":"Note: Publish Draft to WordPress"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Save Execution Metadata\n\nSaves key fields onto the execution record — searchable later in n8n's execution list.\n\nNext: Align Field Names","width":280,"height":232,"color":7},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[2748,520],"id":"1423fca6-31c9-dda8-ee0e-e95844c68265","name":"Note: Save Execution Metadata"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Align Field Names\n\nNormalizes field names so every source feeds the same downstream schema.\n\nNext: Guard Non-Empty content","width":280,"height":232,"color":7},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[3072,520],"id":"a789929a-03bf-3913-282f-54b98389beb5","name":"Note: Align Field Names"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Guard Non-Empty content\n\nDrops items that fail the condition; only qualifying items continue (no false branch).\n\nNext: Summarize Run Stats","width":280,"height":232,"color":7},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[3396,520],"id":"7219ef9d-eaf9-a012-8f51-28f0852ab785","name":"Note: Guard Non-Empty content"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Summarize Run Stats\n\nShapes the item: writes `runAt`, `itemCount`, `status`. Keeps the schema explicit between stages.\n\nNext: Append Audit Row (Google Sheets)","width":280,"height":232,"color":7},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[3720,520],"id":"4041cd04-d2ad-7a7b-f7a8-adac8e4f288f","name":"Note: Summarize Run Stats"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Append Audit Row (Google Sheets)\n\ngoogleSheets — `append` operation against the connected account.\n\nPorts: ①→ Send Summary to Slack · ②→ Capture Failure Context\n\n↻ retries 3×/2s · ⚠ failures exit via the error rail · 🔑 Google OAuth2 / service account","width":280,"height":232,"color":2},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[4044,520],"id":"c757863a-21f1-29d6-0d6e-280c96670f51","name":"Note: Append Audit Row (Google Sheets)"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Send Summary to Slack\n\nslack — `action` operation against the connected account.\n\n↻ retries 3×/2s · ⚠ failures exit via the error rail · 🔑 Slack OAuth2","width":280,"height":232,"color":4},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[4368,520],"id":"40647d22-2dc6-bf69-505a-b948fb66ed50","name":"Note: Send Summary to Slack"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Capture Failure Context\n\nShapes the item: writes `failedNode`, `errorMessage`, `workflow`. Keeps the schema explicit between stages.\n\nNext: Escalate Failure to Slack","width":280,"height":232,"color":3},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[3720,1540],"id":"2d9a3976-7052-6e07-1ef5-888337dda1be","name":"Note: Capture Failure Context"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Escalate Failure to Slack\n\nslack — `action` operation against the connected account.\n\n↻ retries 3×/2s · 🔑 Slack OAuth2","width":280,"height":232,"color":3},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[4044,1540],"id":"0a047d12-07d0-1f41-1191-d8466f1d9fc5","name":"Note: Escalate Failure to Slack"},{"parameters":{"content":"# Produce social posts with Google Drive and WordPress hands-free\n\n**Pattern:** Content Generation · **Level:** Advanced · **Trigger:** Scheduled\n\n## What it does\nProduce social posts with Google Drive and WordPress hands-free. It runs automatically on a schedule.\n\n## Why it exists\nManual cross-posting is slow and error-prone; this workflow makes the process repeatable, monitored and hands-off, with failures surfaced instead of silently lost.\n\n## Main flow\nWeekly Schedule → Stamp & Shape Post → Payload Valid? → Build the Brief → Draft with AI Writer → Refine with AI Editor → Convert to HTML → …\n\n## Use it for\n- Teams that want to content generation without manual effort\n- Anyone automating cross-posting in marketing\n- Replacing a fragile manual process with a reliable workflow\n\n## You get\n- Saves hours of manual work each week\n- Removes copy-paste errors\n- Has retries and error handling built in\n\n## Before first run\nConnect credentials: Google OAuth2 / service account; OpenAI API key; Slack OAuth2; WordPress credentials.\nFollow the color key: 🟦 entry · 🟪 AI · 🟫 actions · ⬜ utilities · 🟩 outputs · 🟥 error rail.\nEach node has its own doc card underneath — read those before editing.","width":480,"height":900},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[-830,80],"id":"c9451e20-c7be-9f92-fb26-e01a7c3cc1ae","name":"📘 Workflow Overview"},{"parameters":{"content":"## 🛟 Error handling & retries\n\nExternal calls retry **3× with 2s backoff**. Anything still failing exits through its node's error output into the red error rail → context is captured and the on-call channel is alerted. Set an n8n **Error Workflow** in settings as the final safety net.","width":360,"height":260,"color":3},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[-230,-20],"id":"ba94fd9d-ab24-4ce2-9f82-6f5a6ce30e34","name":"🛟 Error handling & retries"},{"parameters":{"content":"## 🤖 AI cluster\n\nPurple nodes form one AI unit: the root node orchestrates, sub-nodes plug in via typed ports (model / memory / tools / parser). Swap the chat model without rewiring anything else. Costs scale with tokens — keep prompts lean and cap iterations.","width":360,"height":260,"color":6},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[190,-20],"id":"b57fa5ce-d530-3dc8-8a2b-c82c85f7f367","name":"🤖 AI cluster"},{"parameters":{"content":"## 🛠 Customize me\n\nQuick wins: point the data nodes at your own accounts (see 🔑 lines on each card), adjust the trigger cadence, and tune thresholds/labels to your cross-posting process. Every node card explains its role — safe to extend at any marked branch.","width":360,"height":260,"color":4},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[610,-20],"id":"9c7b10e7-0ea7-46d1-582d-589898c78e1c","name":"🛠 Customize me"}],"connections":{"Weekly Schedule":{"main":[[{"node":"Stamp & Shape Post","type":"main","index":0}]]},"Stamp & Shape Post":{"main":[[{"node":"Payload Valid?","type":"main","index":0}]]},"Payload Valid?":{"main":[[{"node":"Build the Brief","type":"main","index":0}],[{"node":"Record Rejected Input","type":"main","index":0}]]},"Build the Brief":{"main":[[{"node":"Draft with AI Writer","type":"main","index":0}]]},"OpenAI Writer Model":{"ai_languageModel":[[{"node":"Draft with AI Writer","type":"ai_languageModel","index":0}]]},"Draft with AI Writer":{"main":[[{"node":"Refine with AI Editor","type":"main","index":0}],[{"node":"Capture Failure Context","type":"main","index":0}]]},"OpenAI Editor Model":{"ai_languageModel":[[{"node":"Refine with AI Editor","type":"ai_languageModel","index":0}]]},"Refine with AI Editor":{"main":[[{"node":"Convert to HTML","type":"main","index":0}],[{"node":"Capture Failure Context","type":"main","index":0}]]},"Convert to HTML":{"main":[[{"node":"Publish Draft to WordPress","type":"main","index":0}]]},"Publish Draft to WordPress":{"main":[[{"node":"Save Execution Metadata","type":"main","index":0}],[{"node":"Capture Failure Context","type":"main","index":0}]]},"Save Execution Metadata":{"main":[[{"node":"Align Field Names","type":"main","index":0}]]},"Align Field Names":{"main":[[{"node":"Guard Non-Empty content","type":"main","index":0}]]},"Guard Non-Empty content":{"main":[[{"node":"Summarize Run Stats","type":"main","index":0}]]},"Summarize Run Stats":{"main":[[{"node":"Append Audit Row (Google Sheets)","type":"main","index":0}]]},"Append Audit Row (Google Sheets)":{"main":[[{"node":"Send Summary to Slack","type":"main","index":0}],[{"node":"Capture Failure Context","type":"main","index":0}]]},"Capture Failure Context":{"main":[[{"node":"Escalate Failure to Slack","type":"main","index":0}]]},"Send Summary to Slack":{"main":[[],[{"node":"Capture Failure Context","type":"main","index":0}]]}},"active":false,"settings":{"executionOrder":"v1"},"meta":{"templateCredsSetupCompleted":false},"tags":[],"pinData":{},"versionId":"392bbe63-3343-4bc1-b06b-815d06cd5cea","id":"FDX07085"}